## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of recent data and the complexity of isolating factors contributing to the gender pay gap. While the sources provide a comprehensive overview, the nuances of individual experiences and regional differences may not be fully captured. Additionally, the impact of intersectionality, such as race and socioeconomic status, on the gender pay gap requires further exploration.

